body:
Hey everyone! 

I never got the change to thank you all; for all you who favourites my art, I’m super grateful and thankful that you do recognize what I do and take a little time to like it!

Now I’m in the need to ask you to help me, please!

I need to raise $1800 in 5 months to pay for my studies and it’s really important to pay it on time either way they’ll charge me more :‘c 

So this is what I can do for now!

I can do any character from any anime or show you want! That also includes Oc’s if yoy have any! The payment will be through paypal, please!

If you can’t afford paying for a commission you can help me by sharing this! 

or donate a little thing in here: ko-fi.com/A4841663

Anything helps and counts!

Also if you know by any way a better option in here I will be open to hear it!

Thank you for taking your time in reading this! :’)  <3

summary: How would Todoroki, Shinso and Bakugou react to a crush who finds impossible to trust someone romantically? Hope this makes...
question: How would Todoroki, Shinso and Bakugou react to a crush who finds impossible to trust someone romantically? Hope this makes sense D: Thank you for your time 💓
answer:
Thank you for sending a request ❤️


  • Todoroki Shoto: After having had a crush on you for months he was finally ready to confess. He had gotten to know you well, strengthening the bond that he had felt with you since the beginning. When you reject him, explaining to him that you don’t have any trust in relationships after having had bad past experience. He feels sad but respects it. He would ask if you would like to stay friends, telling you that he’ll wait till you are ready.
  • Katsuki Bakugou: As soon as you hit him with ‘I feel the same but…’ he starts becoming embarrassed, wanting to storm off before seeing your eyes tearing up. When you explain your reason to him he feels bad for wanting to stomp away. He tells you that he understands but that you underestimate him, there’s no man like him. You can’t help but smile as he swears to you that he will prove you wrong.
  • Hitoshi Shinso: When he sees your face as he confesses to you he immediately assumes the worst. An awkward silence falls and he curses himself as he sees your body shake, thinking that he has freaked you out. You mumble your reason out to him, admitting that you know that he could be different but that you don’t want to take the risk. Shinso would sit down with you, letting you pour your heart out. Afterwards he would ask you to just go on a few dates with him and see how it would go.
